" --- REST / HTTP Client (<leader>R — kulala.nvim equivalent) ---
nmap <leader>Rr  <Action>(HttpClient.Execute)
nmap <leader>Rs  <Action>(ActivateHTTPClientToolWindow)
nmap <leader>Ri  <Action>(ActivateHTTPClientToolWindow)
